arStrings.szText: {c_label}Lucky Hit:{/c} Damaging enemies with {c_important}Leap{/c}, {c_important}Upheaval{/c}, or {c_important}Whirlwind{/c} have up to a {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} chance to summon an Ancient to perform the same Skill. Can only occur once every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds.
Damaging enemies with {c_important}Leap{/c}, {c_important}Upheaval{/c}, or {c_important}Whirlwind{/c} has a {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} chance to Summon Ancient.
